        "text": "\nBRYSON, Joanna J., 2015. Artificial Intelligence and Pro-Social Behaviour. In: MISSELHORN, Catrin (ed.), Collective Agency and Cooperation in Natural and Artificial Systems: Explanation, Implementation and Simulation. Online. Cham: Springer International Publishing. p.281306. Philosophical Studies Series. [Accessed7June2022]. ISBN978-3-319-15515-9. "
